{"tid":257483,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴爆有建制派常東莞嫖娼專揀處女　中共循此發揚4大方法控制港官議員","createTime":"2017-05-25T09:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T16:34:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"334599b8b4abbc12fd980bace4eb2bb82b753490","tid":257483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/217450/%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4%E7%88%86%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E5%B8%B8%E6%9D%B1%E8%8E%9E%E5%AB%96%E5%A8%BC%E5%B0%88%E6%8F%80%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%BE%AA%E6%AD%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F217450%2F%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%258E%259E%25E5%25AB%2596%25E5%25A8%25BC%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%258F%2580%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25BE%25AA%25E6%25AD%25A4%2F&d=7jD5IsMVw8iSQ%2BRip1nwdp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9eb48cd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/217450/%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4%E7%88%86%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E5%B8%B8%E6%9D%B1%E8%8E%9E%E5%AB%96%E5%A8%BC%E5%B0%88%E6%8F%80%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%BE%AA%E6%AD%A4/</a><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴爆有建制派常東莞嫖娼專揀處女　中共循此發揚4大方法控制港官議員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  訂閱852郵報YouTube頻道<br />\n 2017-5-25 17:11字體： A A A<br />\n大陸流亡富豪郭文貴連日在YouTube發布報平安視頻，並於片中繼續「爆料」，近日則談到香港政要被中共操控的內幕。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴形容，香港的建制派是「賣國派」、「賣港派」，甚至是「嫖娼派」，常到東莞嫖娼，而且專以處女為目標。他又透露，中共控制香港富商、官員及議員有四大方法：（一）搜集貪污行賄證據；（二）引誘他們到大陸嫖娼後拍攝淫亂視頻；（三）中共官二富二代與港商政要做生意，建立利益關係，或偷錄其船上賭博記錄；（四）大規模派人滲入並控制香港各大行業。<br />\n<br />\n另外，郭文貴本周一（22日）也在twitter上談到香港立法會，指「香港有立法會真好」，因為「這是賣港賊們賣掉香港的唯一障礙」。他又呼籲這些年在香港與大陸被公安非法關押抓捕邊控的港人，應為下一代「站出來說話」，否則便是「對後代的嚴重犯罪」。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：郭文貴YouTube影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1ZZ8xWkxFxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1ZZ8xWkxFxA&d=7jD5IsMVw8iSQ%2BRip1nwdp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f70dd33e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1ZZ8xWkxFxA</a>"},{"pid":"1c1d658bb03154a15577d9550ee1b20e03c945da","tid":257483,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59711f2c866b4b1c6fb3833192d78156c49e3973","tid":257483,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"有冇雪x街無碼流出嘅seed先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8691078d80daa37ec5c7724cbb05fd305f6c38","tid":257483,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"處女哩招真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d995890ef39e9dd2a2f533401836916153be399d","tid":257483,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:04:09.000Z","msg":"姓吳個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78676dce556777b61d2f002d4c7db217630374f3","tid":257483,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"何X堯 東莞離隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125722364b8a42ddd503db953254a6f4ea8a0eb4","tid":257483,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"淚灑x廠街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}